      • createOrUpdateAssociate

        public void createOrUpdateAssociate(Associate associate)
        Searches the database to determine if the associate is already included in the database, based on the salesforceId. If found, the updateAssociate(Associate associate) method is called to update the entry. Otherwise, a new entry is made using the createAssociate(Associate associate) method.
        Specified by:
        createOrUpdateAssociate in interface AssociateService
        Parameters:
        associate - An instance of associate without an associateId assigned to it.
        See Also:
        Associate
